{"tid":126573,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣學識揸筷子？","createTime":"2017-02-19T12:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T01:54:35.000Z","uid":31666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"404003d869b8b7f10c070c01775b5bcfbf4a4e4c","tid":126573,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"細個嗰陣唔識諗，覺得夾到野食就ok，一直冇學正確姿勢<br />\n但係大個咗發現正確姿態夾野穩陣好多又美觀啲，同埋覺得同古代啲人一樣咁揸會傳統啲<br />\n所以想問下有冇人都係大個咗先學識揸筷子，可以講下點樣練返好<br />\n仲有想問邊度有嗰啲學揸筷子既筷子賣？"},{"pid":"03a930996f7139f6730ef9a2540e289793b96346","tid":126573,"uid":28769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:50:51.000Z","msg":"學左十幾廿年都學唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c73b0a4414281764fdb90c6f1337bccd627f22","tid":126573,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"揸筆咁揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但已經改唔到"},{"pid":"ea0f54280e6d99ced43bf678be6af3c8cdeb9ab4","tid":126573,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:54:17.000Z","msg":"夾到野就算<br />\n唔算揸得樣衰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但見啲女揸快子好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本只係夾實對快子"},{"pid":"3bdb7b8234b0d94d0c88b9ae2c87d293a4bc9a66","tid":126573,"uid":6760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"細個果時揸唔好 <br />\n俾老豆用筷子兜頭打落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大個左 食完飯係到鬥快夾魚眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db22ad0c118b2ee00d959555182eee05260c0c18","tid":126573,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"睇過youtube學，但試完覺得好攰就好快放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e2bb76a6b5c1897f15a5d624f6f6e677fc03be","tid":126573,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"用刀叉先係文明的象徵"},{"pid":"ca57e57cb3b2e4c7facbb63e86c4ede3f0ff890c","tid":126573,"uid":21533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"逼自己用正確方法 一兩個星期就改左 反而錯嘅方法用唔翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcd22386c38f686f609c3fe0da9e8b5f3e55820","tid":126573,"uid":38833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"中學個陣睇youtube學 練咗一個月就習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5c2f697a9c7181c55e6268cbd6f2314718b89c","tid":126573,"uid":30834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:07:49.000Z","msg":"睇鬼佬啲教學 開頭夾咩都跌 強迫自己揸一個禮拜就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85e032875c545a3f707eac9e467227805057443","tid":126573,"uid":56843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"真係要逼，<br />\n我係細個嘅時候老竇逼出黎，<br />\n以前覺得好多餘，大個咗先知係寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afea1d776e4e8b83937f32af61738b4bf541bc94","tid":126573,"uid":25050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"老豆老母由細教到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日打我隻手 到依家揸得好靚"},{"pid":"870d723ea8e89673048729ce030cfdebe56674a5","tid":126573,"uid":61611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"一直想學揸好筷子 但學唔識<br />\n終於決定係百貨公司買小朋友個種筷子<br />\n有晒圈圈 可以套隻手指落去<br />\n用左個幾星期就學識咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce6c6f25f66fe65971bc0f6d27a50d21751be41","tid":126573,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直想學揸好筷子 但學唔識<br />\n終於決定係百貨公司買小朋友個種筷子<br />\n有晒圈圈 可以套隻手指落去<br />\n用左個幾星期就學識咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度？ 我見到百佳有但係要80蚊好貴"},{"pid":"863693678e5ee8c960f98187dadb3450a5860049","tid":126573,"uid":61611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一直想學揸好筷子 但學唔識<br />\n終於決定係百貨公司買小朋友個種筷子<br />\n有晒圈圈 可以套隻手指落去<br />\n用左個幾星期就學識咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度？ 我見到百佳有但係要80蚊好貴</blockquote><br />\n永安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我買個陣做緊大減價有平 48蚊對<br />\n其實都好貴 不過真係學得識就覺得都算值得"},{"pid":"6a526a9e9f71c1d1c096ad72ad48c193742591cb","tid":126573,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"揸筷子真係隨心<br />\n其實正唔正確又有咩所謂<br />\n最緊要係食到嘢姐<br />\n不過有人話過我揸筷子果陣隻食指會指向天好無禮貌<br />\n之後一兩個禮拜就改咗"},{"pid":"7aed4088fd7de5db7a58db3428b72a84fec3cb9a","tid":126573,"uid":18403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"最近都學緊揸筷子...唔知點解手勢啱 但係夾唔起野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48074ca3e6b0b4396cbf10065e3e49baec58ffc","tid":126573,"uid":30635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"全部屋企人都識渣<br />\n係我細個個時狂屌我 我都唔肯去學<br />\n係對上一個ex教我 叫我學 我先學得識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1113af5e0d5eaaa3cfa2198bd60c525fbba3fe76","tid":126573,"uid":66158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"屋企人教 揸揸下唔啱姿勢<br />\n被人百屌成材"},{"pid":"97a245381ecca817c38a370101f85a77282b3f24","tid":126573,"uid":66158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸筷子真係隨心<br />\n其實正唔正確又有咩所謂<br />\n最緊要係食到嘢姐<br />\n不過有人話過我揸筷子果陣隻食指會指向天好無禮貌<br />\n之後一兩個禮拜就改咗</blockquote><br />\n我屋企人都係教&quot;仆筷&quot;好無禮貌"},{"pid":"ef633e76e8dc555932bf3558ab60ed9819af742d","tid":126573,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己揸得好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日開始迫自己揸哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3245ce543159cb36ca91bb6567c28015ece68b8d","tid":126573,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得自己揸得好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日開始迫自己揸哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗"},{"pid":"82fdfa0a559930a16b3489d6eb2ca267a6fb0296","tid":126573,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"我都係揸左好耐錯手勢，近排先轉番正確揸法，我都係覺得錯手勢唔靚，有依個心態先改到，都係迫自己囉，有依個心態無咁易放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb779065f4f17e796b5f454d40fae68e2dc5d028","tid":126573,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"小學雞嗰陣見到老表可以一路食野一路轉筷子<br />\n覺得好撚型就學左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw正確姿勢好似真係優雅好多<br />\n初頭會覺得發唔到力"},{"pid":"57a7a183314a2b62767b2e468d96c058e8eda9d9","tid":126573,"uid":42180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:08:21.000Z","msg":"當年同同學日日食飯，我地班識揸筷子既都會搶唔識揸筷子既肥牛。<br />\n唔識揸既同學夾魚蛋夾得慢就俾我地幫佢夾起食埋落肚。<br />\n自此個位同學發奮圖強苦練兩星期就搶得翻D肥牛落肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}